about the deadly shootout

1:19:14.010 --> 1:19:16.012
Thursday night
on Station Avenue.

1:19:16.186 --> 1:19:18.884
Police are telling News Center
the gunfire that erupted

1:19:19.058 --> 1:19:21.060
between the two
rival gang members

1:19:21.234 --> 1:19:24.281
left four men dead,
one seriously injured.

1:19:24.455 --> 1:19:27.110
Two of the dead
are known local gang leaders,

1:19:27.284 --> 1:19:29.503
Denzel Ford
and Suarez Hernandez.

1:19:29.677 --> 1:19:30.896
Police are telling us

1:19:31.070 --> 1:19:33.072
