behind the fatal incident.

1:19:39.731 --> 1:19:42.516
Now, in other news today,
school...

1:19:42.690 --> 1:19:46.651
Have you ever wondered how
the infinite God that we serve

1:19:46.825 --> 1:19:48.871
could care about
a single person?

1:19:50.611 --> 1:19:53.310
Hood: I'm here to tell you,
he does.

1:19:53.484 --> 1:19:55.268
I'm here to tell you
that God cares about

1:19:55.442 --> 1:19:57.880
every corner of His creation.

1:19:59.490 --> 1:20:01.187
Think about it.

1:20:01.361 --> 1:20:03.363
How can He keep tabs
of every sparrow

1:20:03.537 --> 1:20:06.976
that He's created and not care
about each and every one of us

1:20:07.150 --> 1:20:09.805
whom He has created
in His own image?

1:20:13.199 --> 1:20:15.419
Today we are going to baptize
these believers

1:20:15.593 --> 1:20:19.989
in the name of the Father
and the Son and the Holy Spirit.

1:20:20.163 --> 1:20:24.428
It will cleanse your souls
of your sins and your worries.

1:20:26.256 --> 1:20:28.867
As the choir sings,
I ask each of you

1:20:29.041 --> 1:20:31.130
who have come for baptism
to follow me.

1:20:31.304 --> 1:20:34.525
Come forth and receive His grace
and His forgiveness.

